JC Flowers May Invest in Spanish Savings Bank, Expansion Reports

-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 
2011-07-06T06:19:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/jc-flowers-may-invest-in-spanish-savings-bank-expansion-reports.html
JC Flowers & Co. offered to invest
400 million euros ($578 million) to 1 billion euros in Spanish
savings bank  Caja de Ahorros del Mediterraneo (CAM)  if a so-called bad
bank is created to take over its real estate-linked assets,
 Expansion  reported, without saying where it obtained the
information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid at 
 abenoit4@bloomberg.net  